message.text:
Calling all FEU Tams! 𝐸𝓁𝓁𝑒'𝓈 𝒥𝑒𝓌𝑒𝓁𝓈 is officially reopening commissions for custom beaded jewelry, with prices starting at just ₱𝟓𝟎! ✨

Whether you want to own accessories to represent your niche interest or a simple design, we've got you covered. Just send us a photo of your design inspiration and we'll bring it to life. 

Each piece is handmade and made to order to ensure you receive a high-quality accessory.

Since every order is custom-made, please note our turnaround time is 1-2 weeks depending on the design and current demand.

₊‧°𐐪♡𐑂°‧₊

💵 Payment:
We accept GCash and bank transfers. A 50% down payment is required when you place your order, with the remaining balance due upon completion.

📦 Delivery:
Pick up your order directly on the FEU campus, or we can arrange for same-day delivery (shipping fee will be shouldered by the buyer).

Check out our updated prices and available designs below! ^__^ 🩷

Message us today to place your order! 😉🩷

message.text:
Calling all FEU Tams! 𝐸𝓁𝓁𝑒'𝓈 𝒥𝑒𝓌𝑒𝓁𝓈 is officially reopening commissions for custom beaded jewelry, with prices starting at just ₱𝟓𝟎! ✨

Whether you want to own accessories to represent your niche interest or a simple design, we've got you covered. Just send us a photo of your design inspiration and we'll bring it to life. 

Each piece is handmade and made to order to ensure you receive a high-quality accessory.

Since every order is custom-made, please note our turnaround time is 1-2 weeks depending on the design and current demand.

₊‧°𐐪♡𐑂°‧₊

💵 Payment:
We accept GCash and bank transfers. A 50% down payment is required when you place your order, with the remaining balance due upon completion.

📦 Delivery:
Pick up your order directly on the FEU campus, or we can arrange for same-day delivery (shipping fee will be shouldered by the buyer).

Check out our updated prices and available designs below! ^__^ 🩷

Message us today to place your order! 😉🩷
